<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5317] CoreAdmin API is not persisting data properly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5317</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a regression between 4.4 and 4.5 with the CoreAdmin API, the command doesn&apos;t save the result on solr.xml at time that is executed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The full process is describe here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://gist.github.com/yriveiro/6883208&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gist.github.com/yriveiro/6883208&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
